name: Debi Mazar
description:
follow me on Instagram, Youtube, Patreon and my website.

Debi Mazar

Suggested Weight: 0.7-1.2

Suggested prompts

  • photo of young d381m4z4r with a-line bob haircut and makeup as a [something], detailed face, skin texture, sharp focus, light bokeh

  • most of the training was from recent images, so to get a younger version add "young" to positive prompts, and try adding "old" and "wrinkles" and etc to the negative prompt

  • Works very well for closeup portraits without inpainting

Training

  • trained on ~24 images

  • Learning Rate: 0.005:1000, 0.001:2000, 0.0001:5000, 0.00005

  • Total Steps: 15,000

  • Batch Size: 1

  • Gradient Steps: 1
